---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Sponsors & Affiliates — DevPlaybook"
  description="Trusted tools and services recommended by DevPlaybook. We only partner with services we use and believe in."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Sponsors & Affiliates</h1>
    <p class="text-text-muted mb-8 text-sm">
      DevPlaybook partners with a small number of trusted services. When you click a referral link and sign up,
      we may earn a commission — <strong class="text-text">at no extra cost to you</strong>.
      <a href="/affiliate" class="text-primary hover:underline ml-1">Full affiliate disclosure →</a>
    </p>

    <!-- Deployment & Hosting -->
    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-1">Deployment & Hosting</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mb-4">Platforms we use to ship and scale applications.</p>
      <div class="space-y-3">

        <a
          href="https://vercel.com/?utm_source=devplaybook&utm_medium=affiliate&utm_campaign=sponsors"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener sponsored"
          class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-bg-card border border-border hover:border-primary/50 rounded-xl p-5 transition-colors group"
        >
          <span class="text-3xl shrink-0">▲</span>
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
              <span class="font-bold text-text group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Vercel</span>
              <span class="text-xs bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 border border-blue-500/20 rounded-full px-2 py-px">Recommended</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">The best way to deploy frontend apps. Zero config, global CDN, instant previews for every PR. Free tier is generous for solo developers.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-primary text-sm font-medium shrink-0 group-hover:underline">Deploy free →</span>
        </a>

        <a
          href="https://railway.app?utm_source=devplaybook&utm_medium=affiliate"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener sponsored"
          class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-bg-card border border-border hover:border-primary/50 rounded-xl p-5 transition-colors group"
        >
          <span class="text-3xl shrink-0">🚂</span>
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
              <span class="font-bold text-text group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Railway</span>
              <span class="text-xs bg-green-500/10 text-green-500 border border-green-500/20 rounded-full px-2 py-px">$5 free credit</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Deploy any app, cron job, or database without touching infrastructure. Postgres, Redis, and custom Docker images out of the box.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-primary text-sm font-medium shrink-0 group-hover:underline">Start free →</span>
        </a>

        <a
          href="https://www.digitalocean.com/?refcode=REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_REFCODE&utm_campaign=Referral_Invite&utm_medium=Referral_Program&utm_source=devplaybook"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener sponsored"
          class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-bg-card border border-border hover:border-primary/50 rounded-xl p-5 transition-colors group"
        >
          <span class="text-3xl shrink-0">🌊</span>
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
              <span class="font-bold text-text group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">DigitalOcean</span>
              <span class="text-xs bg-green-500/10 text-green-500 border border-green-500/20 rounded-full px-2 py-px">$200 credit for new users</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Simple, predictable cloud hosting. Droplets, managed Postgres, App Platform, and Spaces object storage. Trusted by 600,000+ developers.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-primary text-sm font-medium shrink-0 group-hover:underline">Get $200 free →</span>
        </a>

        <a
          href="https://www.hostinger.com/?utm_source=devplaybook&utm_medium=affiliate"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener sponsored"
          class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-bg-card border border-border hover:border-primary/50 rounded-xl p-5 transition-colors group"
        >
          <span class="text-3xl shrink-0">🏠</span>
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
              <span class="font-bold text-text group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Hostinger</span>
              <span class="text-xs bg-yellow-500/10 text-yellow-500 border border-yellow-500/20 rounded-full px-2 py-px">From $2.99/mo</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Affordable shared hosting, VPS, and domain names. Great for WordPress sites, small projects, and landing pages.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-primary text-sm font-medium shrink-0 group-hover:underline">View plans →</span>
        </a>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Databases & Backend -->
    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-1">Databases & Backend</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mb-4">Managed data services for modern applications.</p>
      <div class="space-y-3">

        <a
          href="https://supabase.com/?utm_source=devplaybook&utm_medium=affiliate"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener sponsored"
          class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-bg-card border border-border hover:border-primary/50 rounded-xl p-5 transition-colors group"
        >
          <span class="text-3xl shrink-0">⚡</span>
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
              <span class="font-bold text-text group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Supabase</span>
              <span class="text-xs bg-green-500/10 text-green-500 border border-green-500/20 rounded-full px-2 py-px">Free tier forever</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Open-source Firebase alternative built on Postgres. Includes auth, real-time subscriptions, edge functions, and file storage in one platform.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-primary text-sm font-medium shrink-0 group-hover:underline">Start for free →</span>
        </a>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Disclosure -->
    <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-border text-sm text-text-muted">
      <p>
        All partnerships on this page are affiliate relationships. We may earn a commission when you
        sign up through our links.
        <a href="/affiliate" class="text-primary hover:underline ml-1">Read our full affiliate disclosure →</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
